{"tid":2058243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在囚人士家書","createTime":"2020-06-10T04:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T13:25:34.000Z","uid":67306,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"31b7025c5589c9b951c30185a8cadc8634759645","tid":2058243,"uid":67306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T04:20:13.000Z","msg":"【在囚手足家書】<br />\n<br />\n昨日到白沙灣探望志強手足，從其口中得知在囚期間一切安好，請各位香港人不必擔心。另有一重要資訊，就是他將會於6月12日（抗爭日周年）的時候刑滿。當日早上9:00我會等他出來，志強亦希望有手足到場支持，讓他不至孤單一人。<br />\n<br />\n另外他希望為612不提供捐款一事澄清，不接受612捐款的原因是因為不希望香港人的捐款會落入黨鐵手中，而不是謠言所指612不肯捐錢協助手足。佢亦認為612已經在不同層面協助大量手足，故不要因他的決定而影響抗爭士氣！<br />\n<br />\n志強另有一個請求，希望譚家浚議員能夠在他釋放之前到獄中探訪。他亦非常擔心趙家賢議員及其助理的現況，如情況許可，希望趙議員可來信一封告知他現況如何。<br />\n<br />\n志強寄語香港人要齊心，亦要Be Water。議員們若有信件要寄給手足，建議用議員信封入好（保安理由）。<br />\n請share出去，讓更多香港人看到。<br />\n<br />\n#手足家書<br />\n<br />\n劉家衡"},{"pid":"af6704a9a0de76f9267dda53aac75ea2b64f9af2","tid":2058243,"uid":20908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed820194e782256378c5187eec47c9b4e6761e46","tid":2058243,"uid":262930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2378f2bf2d4f2147f8715d1af5ab38fdfda949","tid":2058243,"uid":67306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T04:25:47.000Z","msg":"自推 希望更多人睇到"},{"pid":"aa3ea41339d41f23140f843709c808cd8ec091b7","tid":2058243,"uid":67306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"c0b6fcb5e05b4d7e777332d313cb8c37d906d77b","tid":2058243,"uid":12831,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"白沙?手足以前坐過監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c132566b86329e721835159cebf5362ca5cf72","tid":2058243,"uid":187232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:04:16.000Z","msg":"以前成日聽人講連登多五毛我依家真係信、一個咁好嘅post都可以沉得咁快、係咪<br />\n受完靶出嚟嘅就唔係手足"},{"pid":"833d34ee8e4593de9ed504f1cf3a94e34870f599","tid":2058243,"uid":187232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:06:28.000Z","msg":"手足受完出嚟淨係想希望有同路人、手足去接佢、唔好一日對住個電腦打**啦、行動下啦、唔係諗住食黃店就當抗爭咗呀"},{"pid":"70ac7010d1838c07b07d9a88f5b85f9ba1b0411c","tid":2058243,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2569a62872f31a14497673158870ef99345c0276","tid":2058243,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"54aa77f936f13543db7bd4852d63f660c8459592","tid":2058243,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcb9068c29f9c5426480083bb7e03d7ef23ac2af","tid":2058243,"uid":67306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:51:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cca06cffc93641441f7fe875b8a77cf5d7b1f7b4","tid":2058243,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2dee37f41ce66ffb489fe9972553c381a104e64","tid":2058243,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"屬於香港人嘅書店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2000687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2000687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1696537ad84a328342206f360ab7bd6c4cb985fa","tid":2058243,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-